/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNNU5FdFFaV0ZxUkhRd05qWlJTRkpVVkdoeGMzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNNU5FdFFaV0ZxUkhRd05qWlJTRkpVVkdoeGMzYxAB!2m1!1s0x89c259c260d1bcf9:0xcc8b9921e7420b07"},{"name":"places/ChIJ-bzRYMJZwokRBwtC5yGZi8w/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25JNVlYVkVReTEzVlV0bmJWUk1Xa2hDVG5WNVVWRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I had a furnace that would not turn on. I called so many places and got the same delays, mind you, it was New Year's Eve, but this company came through with fast, reliable, service. They diagnosed the problem quickly, and furnace will be working again tomorrow. Highly recommended. After this fix, im going to request a whole apartment upgrade for my heating and cooling system. Im rating tgis based on the diagnosis. I dont know what the repair coat is yet, but their diagnosis fee is more than reasonable.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I had a furnace that would not turn on. I called so many places and got the same delays, mind you, it was New Year's Eve, but this company came through with fast, reliable, service. They diagnosed the problem quickly, and furnace will be working again tomorrow. Highly recommended. After this fix, im going to request a whole apartment upgrade for my heating and cooling system. Im rating tgis based on the diagnosis. I dont know what the repair coat is yet, but their diagnosis fee is more than reasonable.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Rim Malinauskas","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104681351036235893164/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWcqF4LeD3J1oYDvsZtox59sD7KUdcCqNzd102kpAzDvppswAyL=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"},"publishTime":"2026-01-02T22:22:05.986428747Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25JNVlYVkVReTEzVlV0bmJWUk1Xa2hDVG5WNVVWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25JNVlYVkVReTEzVlV0bmJWUk1Xa2hDVG5WNVVWRRAB!2m1!1s0x89c259c260d1bcf9:0xcc8b9921e7420b07"},{"name":"places/ChIJ-bzRYMJZwokRBwtC5yGZi8w/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsUFZWVkZNV1F4UTNkcE5qRjVWRlpxT1ZCblJrRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I have trouble with the Frigidaire Ice maker, no ice cube was coming out Sears technician find out that I need a new motor for the Ice maker. Sears technician couldn’t remove the old motor from the tray because they claimed the screw were corroded and after a month of waiting Dmitry K a technician from Gold Fusion HVAC was able to replace the motor and everything is working fine with the Ice maker. Dmitry did an excellent job.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I have trouble with the Frigidaire Ice maker, no ice cube was coming out Sears technician find out that I need a new motor for the Ice maker. Sears technician couldn’t remove the old motor from the tray because they claimed the screw were corroded and after a month of waiting Dmitry K a technician from Gold Fusion HVAC was able to replace the motor and everything is working fine with the Ice maker. Dmitry did an excellent job.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Gregorio Guindin","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106164025149951729007/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLa6mgb-xjg9O53W9EXfNGwULKcVELGaDQmGljuxESvVNWc7w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-12-24T17:39:09.396922330Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsUFZWVkZNV1F4UTNkcE5qRjVWRlpxT1ZCblJrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsUFZWVkZNV1F4UTNkcE5qRjVWRlpxT1ZCblJrRRAB!2m1!1s0x8